      simp_all +decide [← ZMod.intCast_zmod_eq_zero_iff_dvd]
      simp_all +decide [r_K]

/-
The Sieve Isomorphism: Assume x in A_n. By the Fundamental 
Theorem of Arithmetic and the Sieve of Eratosthenes bound from earlier, x survives the Krafft 
